README.md:
seren
=====

SEREN (Hubber et al. 2011; http://arxiv.org/abs/1102.0721) is a self-gravitating Smoothed Particle Hydrodynamics (SPH) code written in Fortran 95/2003 for astrophysical hydrodynamics problems, such as star and planet formation.

For the SEREN webpage, http://dhubber.github.io/seren/
